    <h1>Old online store: mediafinanz</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="admonitionblock important">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-important" title="Important"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Integration only for Callisto online stores</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This page only contains instructions for integrating <strong>mediafinanz</strong> in Callisto online stores. The following instructions are not valid for Ceres online stores!</p>
</div>
</td>
